# Zagorsky, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Zagorsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Chesnokovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 272 as of 2010. There are 5 streets.
Geography
Zagorsky is located 19 km south of Ufa (the district's administrative centre) by road. Chesnokovka is the nearest rural locality.
